Getting Started (2 lines)

    git clone git://github.com/lloydchang/oe-made-easy.git
    cd oe-made-easy && ./core-image-minimal

This bootstraps and cleanly builds core-image-minimal recipe from OpenEmbedded-Core for you :-)
Afterwards, you could use the 'oe-made-easy/oe-core' subdirectory to build incrementally

Please see related documentation (3 links)
http://www.openembedded.org/wiki/OpenEmbedded-Core
https://wiki.yoctoproject.org/wiki/OpenEmbedded-Core
http://cgit.openembedded.org/openembedded-core/tree/meta/recipes-core

